text.div: This code system http://terminology.hl7.org/CodeSystem/epsg-ca defines many codes, but they are not represented here

name: EpsgCa
title: European Petroleum Survey Group Geodetic Parameter Dataset Coordinate Axis

contact.name: International Association of Oil & Gas Producers

description: **Description:**The set of values found in the Coord Axis Code column of the Coordinate Axis table as maintained in the EPSG geodetic parameter dataset. These define the axis for coordinate systems for geographic coordinates.
